{"tid":1815422,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［天地有正氣］我星ching宣佈由我、雞梁、米奇、袁蛇、王蛇組成召妓界勇武小隊正式成立妓小隊係唔智","createTime":"2020-01-07T13:20:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-29T18:38:05.000Z","uid":40856,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"d1e47fbe283e85dc3f1cee0057906b1147e98987","tid":1815422,"uid":40856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:20:35.000Z","msg":"其實我地核心五人早係612已經出黎抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DyHgWPX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDyHgWPX.jpg&h=d013ccdf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係其中四名成員太出名 已經露晒臉(除左本人）<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以我地決定露面 團結大家 比藍屍知道 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>勇武小隊係never die</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n成員一：雞梁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x9TgcpQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx9TgcpQ.jpg&h=1909935a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n主要工作：黑客 黃色戰術分享<br />\n<br />\n成員二：米奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mPcdeEB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmPcdeEB.jpg&h=10a16b75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n主要工作：天使 物資補充<br />\n<br />\n成員三：袁蛇（牙威）<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RTA6zE9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRTA6zE9.jpg&h=de1d8780&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n主要工作： 遠攻手 射眼<br />\n<br />\n成員四：王蛇（俊浩）<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ycjSvf4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FycjSvf4.gif&h=3dfca03f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n主要工作： 內鬼 水魔法（王狗射尿）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>我地想講 無論幾多勇武退出 <br />\n我地召妓小隊都唔會縮</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88af105b15fd466f330c988f9f903dd87b71764f","tid":1815422,"uid":40856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:21:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0157cc4502a0fffa31a0874387845949511b12a","tid":1815422,"uid":40856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:21:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a1d27e7ac2e2b8a5c67b1f367ea7c7275c50474","tid":1815422,"uid":343245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:21:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fa8623383962fb8340e08c0847dccb71a94a8fd","tid":1815422,"uid":40856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:23:05.000Z","msg":"有冇手足想加入"},{"pid":"d756e81915a9f22b4fd0d968ed62456650a2c594","tid":1815422,"uid":189486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:24:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c76a2a746e6b888baa7405ee44b38f7dbb1dd03f","tid":1815422,"uid":40856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:25:10.000Z","msg":"屌 人呢！"},{"pid":"bdd994a5dbcf2cfe71943439514b676a8f4df3ee","tid":1815422,"uid":329466,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:26:27.000Z","msg":"玩得過火左"},{"pid":"fb1a6cf2c5b0d449f2470e42d20c4612adbb92d0","tid":1815422,"uid":71031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:26:41.000Z","msg":"星CHING<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agr